# Documentation: https://github.com/gitleaks/gitleaks#gitleaksignore

# Test data directories with mock credentials
# Excludes common test directory patterns across different project structures
# NOTE: Gitleaks uses REGEX patterns, not glob patterns
.*/testdata/.*
.*/tests/.*
.*/test/.*
.*/__tests__/.*
.*/testing/.*
.*/spec/.*
.*/fixtures/.*

